text: Shah-e-Jahan Chowdhury is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Chittagong-15. ==Career== Chowdhury was elected to parliament from Chittagong-15 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Shah-e-Jahan Chowdhury
